        <Parent_String>floats (finishing equipment) [300023027], tools and equipment for plaster, concrete and mortar working [300022973], equipment by material processed [300168082], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
